env.\n\nWe are happy to get any feedback. More details and screenshots are [in the readme](https://github.com/geometry-zsh/geometry/blob/mnml/readme.md)","files":null},{"type":4,"author":{"id":"940aabe64f74a4490b5129922ab6d0d7b9926a38"},"timestamp":1566382059,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDExOkNsb3NlZEV2ZW50MjU3MjUyNTE4OQ=="},"status":2}]}